WEBVTT

01:42:01.900 --> 01:42:03.734
This is the right mood to kill someone.

01:42:06.984 --> 01:42:08.067
Let me show you something.

01:42:18.567 --> 01:42:19.192
This is it.

01:42:19.734 --> 01:42:24.317
The brushes I made from my victims'
hairs, to paint them, are in this box.

01:42:25.234 --> 01:42:26.359
My treasure.

01:42:28.650 --> 01:42:31.692
The identity which will show
my greatness to this world.
